Package: bayesNMF
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian NMF with Multiple Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Jenna Michelle Landy
Maintainer: Jenna Michelle Landy <jlandy@g.harvard.edu>
Description: Performs Bayesian Non-Negative Matrix Factorization (NMF) with
    various model options. So far, this package implements the
    normal-exponential introduced by Schmidt et al. 2009.
License: MIT License
Encoding: UTF-8
